asset.hookText:
Chrono Classic 1/100 by Victorinox Swiss Army
Ingenuity serving functionality

The Chrono Classic continues to evolve but remains faithful to its 
genetic code. The dimensions and lines that have made it one of the 
brand's bestsellers are still in place. However, a radical transformation 
has taken place at the very heart of the watch, and in the way it 
performs its many functions. The Chrono Classic is now, a "three-way" 
watch.
